Figure 1 shows, for the sake of completeness, the Er-RFL characterization. Figure~1(a) shows the spectrum below and above threshold for different pump powers while Fig.~1(b) shows the linewidth reduction and emitted intensity as a function of pump power. The inset gives a closer view around the threshold pump power, where it can be seen that both the emitted intensity and subtle linewidth narrowing occurs at the same pump power around 3mW.




